title: Ep 2042 - All-in-One Bhai Threatens Bhide
shortDesc: Bhide informs his neighbors that All-in-one bhai is threatening him to not perform Garba festival in Gokuldhan society. Daya informs Jethalal about the issue and requests him to come home at the earliest.

title: Ep 2043 - Jethalal Sells Speakers to All
shortDesc: All-in-one bhai threatens Jethalal and his friends to cancel the garba festival. Iyer and his neighbours learn that Jethalal has sold speakers to All-in-one bhai.

title: Ep 2044 - All-in-One Bhai Threatens Daya and Her Friends
shortDesc: Daya and her friends meet All-in-one bhai. They request him to allow them to organize ‘Garba’ festival in their society. All-in-one bhai refuses to accept their demand.

title: Ep 2045 - Sundar Gifts A Dress to Jethalal
shortDesc: Sundar comes to Jethalal’s house and meets his sister. He brings gifts for Daya and her family. He tells Jethalal that he wishes to purchase a sound system for a garba festival.

title: Ep 2046 - Tappu Sena Ki Chalaki
shortDesc: All-in-one bhai asks the members of Gokuldham society to cancel their garba festival. On the other hand, Tappu Sena plans to disconnect the sound system of All-in-one bhai’s Garba event.

title: Ep 2047 - All In One Bhai Ka Challenge
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham society gather to celebrate Garba festival. On the other hand, All in one bhai organize a mega dandiya event. Will All-in-one bhai allow Jethalal and his neighbours to celebrate the Garba festival?

title: Ep 2048 - Bhide Ka Shirshasana
shortDesc: Madhuri asks Bhide to get some milk but Bhide cut her short by making excuses and change the topic. He faced several obstacles one after another. On the way to bring milk, numerous funny incidents happened with Bhide.

title: Ep 2049 - Jethalal Ka Cheque
shortDesc: Jethalal tells Daya that he is going to Bhide’s house to pay the maintenance charges of the society. Jethalal and Daya come to Bhide’s house. Bhide praises Jethalal for submitting the cheque before the due date.

title: Ep 2050 - Dr. Hathi Ka Injection
shortDesc: Champaklal asks Dr. Hathi to give an injection to Jethalal. Dr. Hathi accidently gives the injection to Bhide.

title: Ep 2051 - Kaveri Ka Phone
shortDesc:
Bhide tells his neighbors that Dr. Hathi accidently gave him an injection. Popatlal receives a call from Kaveri.

title: Ep 2052 - Popatlal Ki Duvidha
shortDesc: Popatlal tells Kaveri that he wishes to marry her. Kaveri clears it to Popatlal that she is a married woman. Kaveri decides to teach Popatlal a lesson for his misbehaviour.

title: Ep 2053 - Popatlal Ki Shaamat
shortDesc: Kaveri and her husband come to Gokuldham society. Kaveri angrily tells Bhide that she wishes to meet Popatlal.

title: Ep 2054 - Popatlal Ka Popat
shortDesc: Popatlal deliberately behaves like a lunatic in front of Kaveri and her family. Kaveri’s husband tells Bhide that he came to Gokuldham Society for his sister’s marriage proposal.

title: Ep 2055 - Kusum Rejects Popatlals Wedding Proposal
shortDesc:
Popatlal requests Kusum to accept his marriage proposal. Kaveri tells Popatlal that he should not have lied to her family.

title: Ep 2056 - Sonu Ka Surprise
shortDesc: Sonu tells Bhide that she wishes to give him a surprise. She requests Bhide to go out of his house for sometime. Bhide comes out of his house and meets his neighbours.
